    MyFundedFutures offers three program types: <strong>Starter</strong>, <strong>Milestone</strong>, and <strong>Expert</strong>. Starter accounts keep it simple with monthly fees and lower contract limits, Milestone accounts have a multi-phase setup with a one-time fee for consistent growth, and Expert accounts offer higher contract limits and bi-weekly payouts for experienced traders.
  </p>

  <!-- Per-challenge summaries -->
  <div class="space-y-3 mb-8">
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Starter – Monthly Fee</p>
      <p>Account sizes of $50K, $100K, and $150K with monthly fees from $80 to $220. EOD drawdown mode with performance-based payouts and a $250 minimum payout threshold.</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-teal-600 font-semibold mt-1">40% consistency rule applies</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Milestone – One-Time Fee</p>
      <p>Account sizes from $25K to $150K with one-time fees from $229 to $665. Multi-phase evaluation with profit targets per phase and a 20% consistency rule.</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-teal-600 font-semibold mt-1">No recurring monthly costs</p>
