    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Expert – Monthly Fee (Higher Limits)</p>
      <p>Account sizes of $50K, $100K, and $150K with monthly fees from $165 to $375. Higher contract limits with time-based bi-weekly payouts and a $1,000 minimum payout.</p>
